title: Sound On: U.S. Deploys Troops to Europe, Fed Hearings

description:
Guests: Retired Lt. General Philip Breedlove, former NATO Supreme Allied Commander and Distinguished Chair of the Frontier Europe Initiative at the Middle East Institute, Bloomberg Economics Editor Michael McKee, and Bloomberg Politics Contributors Jeanne Sheehan Zaino and Rick Davis.
